<p><strong>Tradeoffs:</strong></p>
<p>✔️ Works everywhere (no special fonts)</p>
<p>✔️ Adds negligible overhead</p>
<p>❌ Less pretty than proper icons</p>
<p>❌ Manual extension mapping</p>
